brief_summary.textblock:
      Specific Aims of this study:

        1. To understand the distribution of HDAC4 CNV in the families of the ASD patients with
           HDAC4 CNV;

        2. To perform the analysis of gene expression;

        3. To investigate the HDAC4 protein level expression;

        4. To investigate the correlation of clinical/cognitive features with HDAC4 CNV, RNA and
           protein expression in ASD patients, and compare with their unaffected family members.
